{"id": "cd32b3e2-f2e2-447c-af48-c351ac9b6827", "task_id": "bd4971d8-9e69-47af-9b7b-02016e26e8d4", "path": "backend/templates/index.html", "artifact_type": "file", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>NEO-KYO Login // Access Grid</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ url_for('static', path='/css/style.css') }}\">\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"login-container\">\n        <div class=\"login-glitch-effect\"></div>\n        <h1 class=\"login-title\">NEO-KYO LOGIN</h1>\n        <p class=\"login-subtitle\">_ACCESS GRID_</p>\n\n        {% if error_message %}\n            <div class=\"error-message\">{{ error_message }}</div>\n        {% endif %}\n\n        <form action=\"/login\" method=\"POST\" id=\"loginForm\">\n            <div class=\"input-group\">\n                <label for=\"username\" class=\"input-label\">USERNAME:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"username\" name=\"username\" required autocomplete=\"username\">\n                <span class=\"input-focus-border\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"input-group\">\n                <label for=\"password\" class=\"input-label\">PASSWORD:</label>\n                <input type=\"password\" id=\"password\" name=\"password\" required autocomplete=\"current-password\">\n                <span class=\"input-focus-border\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"login-button\">LOGIN <span class=\"button-glitch\"></span></button>\n        </form>\n\n        <div class=\"login-links\">\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"neon-link\">FORGOT PASSWORD?</a>\n            <span class=\"link-separator\">//</span>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"neon-link\">CREATE ACCOUNT</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <script src=\"{{ url_for('static', path='/js/script.js') }}\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n", "patches": [], "metadata": {"language": "html", "framework": "static_html", "explanation": "This `index.html` file serves as the cyberpunk-themed login page. It includes a standard HTML5 structure with meta tags, a title, and links to external CSS (`style.css`) and JavaScript (`script.js`) files using Jinja2's `url_for` function for proper static asset routing in FastAPI. The page features a central login form with username and password fields, and a submit button. The form is configured with `action=\"/login\"` and `method=\"POST\"` to ensure standard backend processing without JavaScript interception. A conditional Jinja2 block is included to display `error_message` passed from the backend if authentication fails. Decorative elements like 'glitch' effects and neon links are incorporated, relying on accompanying CSS for visual styling.", "dependencies": ["backend/static/css/style.css", "backend/static/js/script.js"]}, "created_at": "2026-06-17 15:55:50.260621"}